<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Lenny LeBlanc, Paul Baloche</author>
<title>Eń joǵary, eń uly..</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.Bb     Eb    F     Bb
 Eń - joǵary, eń - uly!
.Bb     Eb    F     Bb
 Tabıǵattan jáne barlyq adamnan (búkil ǵalamnan)!
.Bb     Gm  Gm7         Eb  Bb
 Danalyqtan, barlyq amaldan!
.Bb/Cm        Eb               F
 Áýel bastan barsyń bar bolǵansyń!

[V2]
.Bb        Eb     F     Bb
 Patshalyqtardan, taqtardan,
.Bb      Eb        F         Bb
 Tańyrqanatyn, bar ǵajaıyptardan!
.Bb     Gm     Gm7         Eb  Bb
 Bar baılyq pen injý-marjannan!
.Bb/Cm          Eb        D/D7
  Eshkim teń kelmes eń ulysyń!

[C1]
.     Bb   Eb  F          Bb
   Shegelendi, qabirde jatty!
.  Bb   Eb   F          Bb
   Ólý úshin, ómirge keldi!
.  Bb     Gm     Gm7         Eb  Bb
   Solǵan gúldeı, taptalǵan meni,
.  Bb    Cm         Eb/F
   Jany ashyp, kóterdi,
.  F7    Bb
   Eń - uly!</lyrics>
</song>